data.description: Just right! VA Assumable Loan @ 3.125% available…. This ARBORDALE townhome at 2 years young has great contemporary design features. The exterior’s clean lines present windows that flood the interior with natural light. Its interior open concept floor plan is perfect for entertaining. The main living area features a spacious great room with sliding glass doors to the back yard; and gleaming kitchen with stainless steel appliances, oversized island with seating, excellent counter space and cabinetry. Upstairs, there are three bedrooms, including the primary suite with a tray ceiling, an ensuite bathroom, and walk-in closet.  The finishes throughout the home are beautiful with luxury vinyl flooring, granite countertops, and all new carpet. 324 Capeside court is a beautiful home that offers the best in modern living at an affordable price with great location.
